  "title": "ADMIN ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle daily administrative tasks including filing, documentation, and data entry</p></li><li><p>Assist recruitment consultants with candidate profiles, resume screening, and system updates</p></li><li><p>Coordinate interview schedules and send interview confirmations</p></li><li><p>Prepare offer letters, employment contracts, and onboarding documents</p></li><li><p>Maintain employee and candidate records accurately</p></li><li><p>Support basic HR, payroll, and claims administration (if required)</p></li><li><p>Handle incoming calls, emails, and basic communication with clients and candidates</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad-hoc administrative duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or relevant working experience</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in recruitment, HR, or administrative roles is an advantage. Welcome fresh graduate, we provide training.</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook)</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented, organized, and responsible</p></li><li><p>Basic English communication skills (written and spoken)</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li></ul><p><strong>Preferred / Advantage</strong></p><ul><li><p>Familiarity with basic HR processes in Singapore</p></li></ul>",
